(48, 5, 5, 5, 'Exercise 2', NULL, 'exercise-2', 'Page 19', '<p>Use the contractions <strong>wasn\'t</strong> or <strong>weren\'t</strong> to complete the following negative sentences.</p>\r\n<p>My marks ___ good at school last year.</p>\r\n<p>It ___ a raccoon; it was a skunk.</p>\r\n<p>The stain on the floor ___ big.</p>\r\n<p>The vegetables ___ fresh.</p>\r\n<p>You ___ very polite with the landlord.</p>\r\n<p>It ___ the right answer.</p>\r\n<p>The horn in my car ___ loud.</p>\r\n<p>We ___ at the funeral.</p>\r\n<p>The kids ___ quiet today in class.</p>\r\n<p>The grass ___ long.</p>\r\n<p>She ___ very clever.</p>\r\n<p>The lake ___ deep.</p>\r\n<p>The baby ___ in the stroller.</p>\r\n<p>He ___ on the table.</p>\r\n<p>My socks ___ on the clothesline.</p>\r\n<p>The shaver ___ in the bathroom.</p>\r\n<p>The bread and butter ___ on the counter.</p>\r\n<p>The museum ___ very big.</p>\r\n<p>The rats ___ in the cellar.</p>\r\n<p>The nest ___ on the ground.</p>\r\n<p>I ___ on the phone.</p>\r\n<p>It ___ a big snowstorm.</p>\r\n<p>The binders ___ in my locker.</p>\r\n<p>The man ___ Greek; he was Italian.</p>\r\n<p>The jam ___ in the fridge.</p>\r\n<p>It ___ a good movie.</p>\r\n<p>The lights ___ on.</p>\r\n<p>The stove ___ off.</p>\r\n<p>It ___ ugly.</p>\r\n<p>The cat ___ black.</p>\r\n<p>The hammer ___ in the toolbox.</p>\r\n<p>The powder ___ on the shelf.</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-21 04:38:10', '2019-07-21 04:43:34'),
