(25, 5, 1, 3, 'Exercise 1', NULL, 'exercise-1', 'Using the correct form of To Be', '<p>Rewrite the following sentences to create the present tense by choosing the correct form of the verb <strong>To Be</strong> in parentheses.</p>\r\n<p>The girl [am, is, are] pretty. - is</p>\r\n<p>I [am, is, are] ready. - am</p>\r\n<p>She [am, is, are] my friend. - is</p>\r\n<p>They [am, is, are] twins. - are</p>\r\n<p>The flowers [am, is, are] yellow. - are</p>\r\n<p>The flashlight [am, is, are] in the tent. - is</p>\r\n<p>The fridge and counter in the kitchen [am, is, are] dirty. - are</p>\r\n<p>I [am, is, are] tired today. - am</p>\r\n<p>We [am, is, are] busy. - are</p>\r\n<p>The toys [am, is, are] in the basement. - are</p>\r\n<p>The ribbons in my hair [am, is, are] pink. - are</p>\r\n<p>The kitchen [am, is, are] very small. - is</p>\r\n<p>The vacuum [am, is, are] in the closet. - is</p>\r\n<p>He [am, is, are] nice. - is</p>\r\n<p>The microwave oven [am, is, are] in the kitchen. - is</p>\r\n<p>The toy [am, is, are] on the floor. - is</p>\r\n<p>I [am, is, are] sick today. - am</p>', 1, 42, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'prompt=\"Select the missing word:\"; font-size=\"200%\";', NULL, NULL, '2019-07-19 01:59:02', '2019-07-30 21:14:46'),
