(169, 5, 27, 3, 'Exercise 1', NULL, 'exercise-2', NULL, '<p>Rewrite the following sentences to express the negative form.&nbsp; Write the sentence once using <strong>was not</strong> or <strong>were not</strong> and once using the contractions <strong>wasn\'t</strong> or <strong>weren\'t</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>There was a crack in my windshield. - There was not a crack in my windshield.</p>\r\n<p>There was a crack in my windshield. - There wasn\'t a crack in my windshield.</p>\r\n<p>There were many shells and stones in the sand on the beach. - There were not many ...</p>\r\n<p>There were many shells and stones in the sand on the beach. - There weren\'t many ...</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 05:02:52', '2019-07-26 05:05:25'),
