(194, 5, 32, 3, 'Exercise 1', NULL, 'exercise-1', NULL, '<p>Rewrite the following sentences to create the question form of the present progressive tense by placing the verb <strong>To Be</strong> before the subject.&nbsp; Don\'t forget to include a question mark (?) in your answer.</p>\r\n<p>They are talking about the newborn baby. - Are they talking?</p>\r\n<p>He is hunting with a bow and arrow. - Is he hunting?</p>\r\n<p>I am rocking the boat. - Are you rocking the boat?</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:20:07', '2019-07-26 22:22:35'),
(195, 5, 32, 4, 'Vocabulary List 2', NULL, 'vocabulary-list-2', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:22:44', '2019-07-26 22:22:44'),
(196, 5, 32, 5, 'Exercise 2', NULL, 'exercise-2', NULL, '<p>Rewrite the following sentences to create questions in the present progressive tense by placing the verb <strong>To Be</strong> before the subject.</p>\r\n<p>Tom is spying on us. - Is Tom spying on us?</p>\r\n<p>I am failing my science class. - Am I failing my science class?</p>\r\n<p>The children are bursting the balloons. - Are the children bursting the balloons?</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:22:57', '2019-07-26 22:24:50'),
(197, 5, 33, 1, 'The Past Progressive (Continuous) Tense', NULL, 'the-past-progressive--continuous--tense', NULL, '<p>The past progressive is used to describe an activity that happened and continued for a period of time in the past.&nbsp; It is formed using the past tense of the verb <strong>To Be</strong> and by adding <strong>-ing</strong> to the simple form of the verb.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-borderless\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >I am using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >I was using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >I was using the stove.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >you are using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >You were using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >You were using my stapler.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >he is using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >He was using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >He was using my car.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >she is using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >She was using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >She was using my makeup.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >it is using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >It was using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >It was using its paws.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >we are using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >We were using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >We were using the glue.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >they are using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >They were using</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >They were using the laptop.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:25:22', '2019-07-26 22:28:44'),
(198, 5, 33, 2, 'Vocabulary List 1', NULL, 'vocabulary-list-1', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:28:54', '2019-07-26 22:28:54'),
(199, 5, 33, 3, 'Exercise 1', NULL, 'exercise-1', NULL, '<p>Rewrite the following sentences to form the past progressive tense.&nbsp; Use the correct past tense form of the verb <strong>To Be</strong> and add <strong>-ing</strong> to the simple form of the verb in parenthesis.</p>\r\n<p>The laboratory (to test) the blood for AIDS and other diseases. - was testing</p>\r\n<p>We (to walk) in the snow with our snowshoes. - were walking</p>\r\n<p>I (to change) the lightbulb when I got a shock. - was changing</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:28:59', '2019-07-26 22:31:47'),
(200, 5, 33, 4, 'Vocabulary List 2', NULL, 'vocabulary-list-2', NULL, '', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:31:57', '2019-07-26 22:31:57'),
(201, 5, 33, 5, 'Exercise 2', NULL, 'exercise-2', NULL, '<p>Complete the following sentences to form the past progressive tense.&nbsp; Use the correct past tense form of the verb <strong>To Be</strong> and add <strong>-ing</strong> to the simple form of the verb in parentheses.</p>\r\n<p>The flowers ___ (to bloom) in the garden. - were blooming</p>\r\n<p>Raul ___ (to eat) pork and beans. - was eating</p>\r\n<p>The eggs ___ (to hatch). - were hatching</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:32:03', '2019-07-26 22:34:17'),
(202, 5, 34, 1, 'The Past Progressive (Continuous) Tense: Negative Form', NULL, 'the-past-progressive--continuous--tense--negative-form', NULL, '<p>Place <strong>not</strong> after the past tense form of the verb <strong>To Be</strong> to create the negative form of the past progressive tense.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-borderless\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >I was moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >I was not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >I was not moving my leg.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >you were moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >you were not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >You were not moving it.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >he was moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >he was not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >He was not moving his pen.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >she was moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >she was not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >She was not moving her lips.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >it was moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >it was not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >It was not moving its tail.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >we were moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >we were not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >We were not moving our car.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >they were moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >they were not moving</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >They were not moving it.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>The negative form of the past progressive tense can also be expressed with the contaction <strong>wasn\'t</strong> or <strong>weren\'t</strong>.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-borderless\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >I was not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >I wasn\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >I wasn\'t helping him.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >you were not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >you weren\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >You weren\'t helping me.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >he was not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >he wasn\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >He wasn\'t helping his aunt.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >she was not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >she wasn\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >She wasn\'t helping the nurse.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >it was not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >it wasn\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >It wasn\'t helping us.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >we were not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >we weren\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >We weren\'t helping her.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >they were not helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >they weren\'t helping</td>\r\n<td >&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td >They weren\'t helping them.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:34:50', '2019-07-26 22:40:31'),
