(204, 5, 34, 3, 'Exercise 1', NULL, 'exercise-1', NULL, '<p>Rewrite the following sentences to create the negative form of the past progressive tense.&nbsp; Write your answer once with <strong>was not</strong> or <strong>were not</strong> and once with the contraction <strong>wasn\'t</strong> or <strong>weren\'t</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>She was getting treatments for cancer. - was not getting</p>\r\n<p>She was getting treatments for caner. - wasn\'t getting</p>\r\n<p>We were driving on the road. - were not driving</p>\r\n<p>We were driving on the road. - weren\'t driving</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:40:55', '2019-07-26 22:43:25'),
