(206, 5, 34, 5, 'Exercise 2', NULL, 'exercise-2', NULL, '<p>Complete the following sentences using the contraction <strong>wasn\'t</strong> or <strong>weren\'t</strong> to complete the following sentenses in the negative past progressive form.&nbsp; Add <strong>-ing</strong> to the simple form of the verb in parentheses.</p>\r\n<p>He ___ (to snip) the black wire. - wasn\'t snipping</p>\r\n<p>You ___ (to overdo) it. - weren\'t overdoing</p>\r\n<p>I ___ (to taste) your dessert. - wasn\'t tasting</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:43:42', '2019-07-26 22:46:19'),
(207, 5, 35, 1, 'The Past Progressive (Continuous) Tense: Question Form', NULL, 'the-past-progressive--continuous--tense--question-form', NULL, '<p>Place the past tense form of the verb To Be before the subject to create questions in the past progressive tense.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-borderless\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >I was swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >was I swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Was I swimming well?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >you were swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >were you swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Were you swimming alone?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >he was swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >was he swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Was he swimming with you?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >she was swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >was she swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Was she swimming at night?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >it was swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >was it swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Was it swimming in the bath?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >we were swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >were we swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Were you swimming better?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td >they were swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >were they swimming</td>\r\n<td >&rarr;</td>\r\n<td >Were they swimming fast?</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-26 22:47:03', '2019-07-26 22:49:44'),
