(237, 5, 40, 3, 'Exercise 1', NULL, 'exercise-1', NULL, '<p>Rewrite the following sentences in the future tense using <strong>be going to</strong>.&nbsp; Use the correct form of the verb <strong>To Be</strong> and the simple form of the verb in parenthesis.</p>\r\n<p>I (be) going to (to hurry) because I don\'t want to miss my bus. - am</p>\r\n<p>He drank too much and now he (be) going to (to vomit). - is</p>\r\n<p>You (be) going to (to dirty) my floor with your muddy feet. - are</p>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-07-27 20:21:07', '2019-07-27 20:23:58'),
