(303, 11, 1, 1, 'Introduction', NULL, 'introduction', NULL, '<p id=\"303.1\">The best way to learn English is to build your vocabulary, learn the verb tenses and the basic grammar rules, and then practice listening, speaking, and reading as much as possible.</p>\r\n<p id=\"303.2\">The goal of this course is to avoid long grammar explanations by showing the concepts in simple terms so that the student can focus on learning quickly and practice speaking and listening.</p>\r\n<div class=\"lesson-note\">\r\n<p id=\"303.3\"><strong>Note:</strong> English is the most widely spoken language worldwide, with 1.5 billion speakers.&nbsp; It is the&nbsp;standard language for business, technology, and tourism.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-08-07 23:16:46', '2019-10-14 17:02:03'),
